mpit.co.kr/images/stacks/noStack.png" alt="Spark" width="20" height="20" style="margin-right:6px;vertical-align:bottom;"> Spark</span><span style="display:inline-block;margin:0 6px 6px 0;padding:6px;border-radius:3px;background:#f4f4f4;font-size:15px;color:#000;line-height:20px;"><img src="https://cdn.jumpit.co.kr/images/stacks/hadoop.png" alt="Hadoop" width="20" height="20" style="margin-right:6px;vertical-align:bottom;"> Hadoop</span><span style="display:inline-block;margin:0 6px 6px 0;padding:6px;border-radius:3px;background:#f4f4f4;font-size:15px;color:#000;line-height:20px;"><img src="https://cdn.jumpit.co.kr/images/stacks/noStack.png" alt="Etl" width="20" height="20" style="margin-right:6px;vertical-align:bottom;"> Etl</span><span style="display:inline-block;margin:0 6px 6px 0;padding:6px;border-radius:3px;background:#f4f4f4;font-size:15px;color:#000;line-height:20px;"><img src="https://cdn.jumpit.co.kr/images/stacks/noStack.png" alt="Tableau" width="20" height="20" style="margin-right:6px;vertical-align:bottom;"> Tableau</span>                </dd>
